    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a suitable budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. While the car is currently operational and drives, the exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several paint chips, minor dents, and some surface rust on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining from regular use. Mechanically, it remains functional, though you should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items like brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a reliable starter car but is sold as-is to reflect its current state.",
