    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Prepare to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This car is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously cared for and is essentially flawless, making it a rare find for anyone seeking a like-new experience. You won't find a more pristine or well-preserved example anywhere!",
