      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a solid ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
