    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The double-VANOS system has been serviced with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and new trailing arm bushings to ensure the suspension geometry remains precise. The M-Variable limited-slip differential provides excellent lock-up under load, and the engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders. Mechanically robust and ready for the apex, this example shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver's car.",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2020 Sedan. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title in hand. No mechanical issues. Cash only.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
